{"tid":1859561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲將由武漢回國公民送到聖誕島隔離","createTime":"2020-02-03T09:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T11:04:21.000Z","uid":54800,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"664d3b2f94ff66ba803130b78625935725c7fbc3","tid":1859561,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"澳洲政府開始將由中國武漢返國的公民及永久居民，送到距離本島2700公里的聖誕島隔離檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n首批243人乘坐包機，抵達西澳州的空軍基地後，轉乘另一班機到聖誕島，他們需要在原本用作拘留移民的中心，隔離14日。<br />\n<br />\n不少原本滯留武漢的澳洲人，對拘留中心的醫療設施及環境表示質疑，又批評政府要求他們每人支付1000澳元的撤離費。當局後來改口願意承擔費用，並派出由24名醫護人員組成的專家小組到聖誕島。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲至今確診12宗新型肺炎病例，其中3人已經康復，並已經出院。"},{"pid":"aeac0986914a2119bcd588fbe77ec785b3419f42","tid":1859561,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27444825c5e89ce800ba977608ff6a6a36d99981","tid":1859561,"uid":194326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://discordemoji.com/assets/emoji/1717_Crab_Rave.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscordemoji.com%2Fassets%2Femoji%2F1717_Crab_Rave.gif&h=ddedf691&s={SIZE}\" /> ISOLATED <img src=\"https://discordemoji.com/assets/emoji/1717_Crab_Rave.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscordemoji.com%2Fassets%2Femoji%2F1717_Crab_Rave.gif&h=ddedf691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b73b9576692b98b978783e24ba37775c037af80a","tid":1859561,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27444825c5e89ce800ba977608ff6a6a36d99981","tid":1859561,"uid":194326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://discordemoji.com/assets/emoji/1717_Crab_Rave.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscordemoji.com%2Fassets%2Femoji%2F1717_Crab_Rave.gif&h=ddedf691&s={SIZE}\" /> ISOLATED <img src=\"h